      mesmerising in-depth series on Dream of the Red Chamber 紅樓夢 - akin to
      the late
      <a href="https://blog.frankdelaney.com/re-joyce/" target="_blank"
        >Frank Delaney's contribution</a
      >
      to James Joyce's Ulysses - essays on Buddhism, and musings on artistic
      expression across differing cultural and societal values.
    </p>
    <p>
      Transcriptions of three episodes from Chiang Xun's
      <a
        href="https://open.firstory.me/user/cktxxrlw27ioo0898okcvd43b"
        target="_blank"
